{"tid":1375293,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"8月5號7區集會係邊個諗出黎？","createTime":"2019-07-28T04:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T06:42:17.000Z","uid":94075,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d113e4482ba68bec912963c388cd40c5b27e45b7","tid":1375293,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CjLbsEK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCjLbsEK.png&h=e10aa174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說今日係朋友tg谷見到呢條message <br />\n<br />\n我呆一呆 我日日都有上連登 但未見過有人講呢個7區罷工 先唔懷疑有有心人想分薄人力 遍地開花係好事 但有冇諗過人數問題？由71開始我地已經不斷講 人多就安全 但大家都知其實我地集會 遊行嘅人數愈黎愈少 好似琴日咁都係得廿八萬人左右 呢條數將佢除7 人數係咪少好多？啲狗要圍我地又係咪易好多？同埋地點分散咁多 如果有兩三區同時有事 想幫手嘅手足就會好亂 唔知去邊區幫手好 同埋未必每區都可以整到物資站<br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲集思廣益 如果大家認為呢個方法可行嘅 okay 我會無條件支持 但如果覺得唔work 請大家幫手澄清番冇人推呢個方法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"baa16de327f734ac2f1cc111f9c3154e73475e9f","tid":1375293,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:27:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb5e7c6962e2ebe6015f74f10945b1c0188ff7fb","tid":1375293,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:27:18.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"2f118ca79c242c7b5bdce5684fdee9417c1bda21","tid":1375293,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e5996475541b0970c4e3c723d4b40ce86837e1fa","tid":1375293,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:29:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"567c6e0f18bf9dc20854a0c65825a28e8e5e16c5","tid":1375293,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"91aa91d96656e0cba7431b847da343802dd34320","tid":1375293,"uid":278029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"無聽過，聲勢仲弱過今日上環集會"